{"tid":658644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖)實驗：被連仔網上欺淩的植物, 三十天後 生長會出現劇變？","createTime":"2018-05-09T07:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T10:52:20.000Z","uid":36502,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f738d82f6307341f280b70714b37dc18f7ad2830","tid":658644,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T07:11:10.000Z","msg":"兩株植物放在家中，其中一株植物會被連登仔讚美，相反另一株則會被網上欺淩網上欺淩。接著30天後，看看兩株植物是否有所差異。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除了欺淩與讚美的差別，兩株植物其他生長環境完全相同，像是每天澆同樣的水、被陽光照射，並給予肥料。<br />\n<br />\n看看30天後，令人印象深刻的結果解釋了一切！左邊是被連仔網上欺淩的植物，右邊是被讚美的植物。差異是否真的很明顯？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/150752_c739c4cc8b694c74bfd518e20a00dd44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F150752_c739c4cc8b694c74bfd518e20a00dd44.jpg&h=49c9b364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/150716_980806d97986c9debbbf750e990548ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F150716_980806d97986c9debbbf750e990548ff.jpg&h=d71af8a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被讚美的植物繼續茁壯生長，而被欺淩的植物明顯在掙紮，有著棕色的葉子並且看起來了無生氣。<br />\n<br />\n連植物都受不了，況且是人，原來被連仔網上欺淩的會影響很大!"},{"pid":"4b32d850a65d1c557ffff07aac76fb9e733b29ed","tid":658644,"uid":65743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T07:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/152040_2baf8f395017f385bfbed6749ba633b3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F152040_2baf8f395017f385bfbed6749ba633b3.gif&h=26bd3283&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66c7af0c2424038d389b3152f352e830a106c578","tid":658644,"uid":162268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T07:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f660739e257d9726d3a690a272166b3523b551","tid":658644,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T07:21:53.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"1c2b4f805455e5567108ab4dfc490dfb28e2a33b","tid":658644,"uid":71441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T07:27:55.000Z","msg":"做啲有建設性嘅嘢得嘛"},{"pid":"c7695c9a65eaf6d0c5ddda445897dab771267724","tid":658644,"uid":30347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:23:52.000Z","msg":"被望遠網上欺淩嘅話，會有咩影響？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a80d04a49ccdcee32b98e9ae01eef46a82d8b03","tid":658644,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:27:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"232e114ebf7c2379203a51101bbb346b8de2c5f9","tid":658644,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7a80d04a49ccdcee32b98e9ae01eef46a82d8b03","tid":658644,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:27:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:57:08.000Z","msg":"你原創架個實驗？"},{"pid":"eb6226f1cb85e6d653e6912c7be13b3599245f44","tid":658644,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:11:29.000Z","msg":"content farm文章都要爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf4d8ee21d4b642db0625122b22ff950afb3625","tid":658644,"uid":26752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/6e0c970a6dbbf5c0c643e0e96ce35230/tenor.gif?itemid=7676808\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F6e0c970a6dbbf5c0c643e0e96ce35230%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D7676808&h=37667df1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c8501798271a00e4b6d8b0a43b01e553b595278","tid":658644,"uid":55924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:28:18.000Z","msg":"植物識上網<br />\n不如話佢上咸網啦"},{"pid":"0920aebb